    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. This car has been a reliable daily driver, and its condition reflects a history of responsible ownership. The exterior boasts a deep, glossy finish with only minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the premium leather upholstery remains supple and free of any punctures or tears, though there is light, natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every electronic feature, from the responsive infotainment system and dual-zone climate control to the heated seats, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in excellent working order; it has received full synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles and recently passed a comprehensive multi-point inspection. The tires have approximately 75% tread remaining, and the brake pads were replaced within the last year, providing firm, confident stopping power. This vehicle comes with a clean title, a smoke-free interior, two sets of keys, and a complete folder of service records. It is a solid, honest example of the model, ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately without any looming maintenance concerns.",
      "price": 34500.0,
