      "description": "Experience the pinnacle of BMW\u2019s naturally aspirated era with this E46 M3. Under the hood, the S54 inline-six features individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing, providing instantaneous throttle response and a high-revving 8,000 RPM ceiling. Power is delivered via a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a torque-sensing limited-slip rear differential. This example boasts a reinforced subframe and documented rod bearing service, ensuring the structural integrity matches its mechanical prowess. The chassis dynamics remain sharp, offering the tactile feedback and near 50/50 weight distribution that defined a generation. It presents in honest, driver-grade condition, ready for the canyon roads.",
